                <mxCell id="title" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Azure Managed App + Container Offer Architecture&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Managed Application deploys the infrastructure (AKS, Redis, VNet, Identity).&lt;br&gt;The Container Offer deploys the application (Helm chart via K8s Extension) onto AKS.&lt;br&gt;This pattern enables billing for both infrastructure management &lt;i&gt;and&lt;/i&gt; application IP." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=5;spacingTop=5;" parent="1" vertex="1">
